org.jasig.cas.client.validation.TicketValidator
public class Cas20ServiceTicketJsonValidator
extends org.jasig.cas.client.validation.Cas20ServiceTicketValidator

An implementation of the Cas20ServiceTicketValidator that expects the ticket validation response to be a JSON string, represented by TicketValidationJsonResponse that is rendered by ServiceValidateSuccessJsonView. On success, it returns an instance of Assertion object that is populated with ticket data and attributes, if any.

Since:
0.6
Author:
Misagh Moayyed, Unicon, inc.
